		</Group>
		<RichText x="738" y="511" width="434" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffedbf">(仅大世界)<span color="#ffffff">战斗场地周围存在7种元素的小型史莱姆。入战时，虹彩史莱姆将直接吸收这些史莱姆，每个史莱姆为</span><span textDecoration="underline" color="#ffffff">虹色辉光</span><span color="#ffffff">提供</span><span color="#ffdfbf">2</span><span color="#ffffff">点充能。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="424" height="172" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" textDecoration ="underline" color="#ffffff">虹色辉光<span textDecoration="none">满时，虹彩史莱姆将立即变大进入「聚光」状态并产生</span><span textDecoration="none" color="#ffdfbf">30</span><span textDecoration="none">枚白色微粒；该状态下不吸收能量，且每受到</span><span textDecoration="none" color="#ffdfbf">11.667%生命值</span><span textDecoration="none">的伤害就会塌缩一次，每次均产生</span><span textDecoration="none" color="#ffdfbf">8</span><span textDecoration="none">枚白色微粒，至多塌缩3次，随后瘫痪6s(吃人算第一次塌缩)。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="511" width="439" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffdfbf">聚光<span color="#ffffff">状态下，虹彩史莱姆靠近玩家，将其一把吃掉，玩家将被控制并持续</span><span textDecoration="underline" color="#ffffff">流血</span><span color="#ffffff">直至挣脱。挣脱或自行退出时，虹彩史莱姆将塌缩一次，产生</span><span>8</span><span color="#ffffff">枚白色微粒，并失去</span><span>5%</span><span color="#ffffff">生命值。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="767" width="434" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffdfbf">聚光<span color="#ffffff">状态下，虹彩史莱姆喷发史莱姆凝胶，凝胶落地后造成</span><span color="#ffffbf">39%</span><span color="#ffffff">的对应元素伤害，且有</span><span>18%</span><span color="#ffffff">概率召唤对应史莱姆(草史莱姆为</span><span>8%</span><span color="#ffffff">)，最多连续喷发5次，在场的召唤史莱姆不超过5只。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="1023" width="436" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffdfbf">聚光<span color="#ffffff">状态下，虹彩史莱姆凝聚无瑕之力，高速旋转自身并下压产生3波冲击波，对范围内目标造成</span><span color="#b8b8b8">100%</span><span color="#ffffff">伤害，命中召唤的史莱姆时将其击杀。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="1247" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">虹彩史莱姆靠近角色进行一次撞击，造成<span color="#ffffbf">30%</span><span>的对应元素伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="767" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">虹彩史莱姆靠近角色进行下落攻击，根据自身吸收的属性，下落产生的效果也不相同。属性为空时不攻击。</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="1164" width="442" height="154" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">仅属性为<span color="#7fffd7">风元素</span><span>时无自附着。<br/>聚光变大时，抗打断0，质量翻3倍；</span><span color="#ffdfbf">击退或击飞的攻击</span><span>会使其进入</span><span color="#ffdfbf">9.5s</span><span>的韧性保护期，此时抗打断0.066。<br/>虹色辉光：满计量200，</span><span color="#ffdfbf">1:1</span><span>转换吸收的</span><span color="#ffdfbf">元素能量</span><span>，忽视</span><span color="#ffbfbf">特殊能量</span><span>；受到非免疫的元素攻击时按照</span><span color="#ffdfbf">所受攻击元素</span><span>的量积攒</span><span color="#ffdfbf">1.875n%</span><span>(3.75n)或</span><span color="#ffdfbf">0.15%</span><span>(0.3)计量，攒满后进入聚光变大状态，该状态下不再吸收元素能量。<br/>流血：角色每</span><span color="#ffdfbf">0.3s</span><span>失去</span><span color="#ffdfbf">3.5%</span><span>生命值。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="436" height="172" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">虹彩史莱姆每隔7-10s汲取一次前台的<span color="#ffdfbf">元素能量</span><span>，将其以</span><span color="#ffdfbf">1:1</span><span>转化为</span><span textDecoration="underline">虹色辉光</span><span>的充能，汲取期间将切换自身属性为</span><span color="#ffdfbf">前台角色元素获得对应免疫及自附着</span><span>；受到</span><span color="#ffdfbf">非免疫元素伤害</span><span>时可为</span><span textDecoration="underline">虹色辉光</span><span>充能。单次吸收不超过100点元素能量。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
